{"title_page": "Aaron ben Isaac of Rechnitz", "text_new": "'''Aaron ben Isaac of [[Rechnitz]]''' was the author of a midrashic commentary on the Bible, the first portion of which (Genesis) was published in 1786 at [[Sulzbach-Rosenberg|Sulzbach]] under the title \"Bet Aharon\" (House of Aaron).<ref>{{JewishEncyclopedia|inline=1|article=AARON BEN ISAAC OF RECHNITZ|url=http://www.jewishencyclopedia.com/articles/44-aaron-ben-isaac-of-rechnitz|author=Louis Ginzberg|authorlink=Louis Ginzberg|accessdate=Oct 16, 2017}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:ben Isaac of Rechnitz, Aaron}}\n[[Category:18th-century German writers]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n[[Category:German Jews]]\n[[Category:German biblical scholars]]\n[[Category:18th-century Jews]]\n[[Category:Authors of Rabbinic works]]\n[[Category:Bible commentators]]\n[[Category:German male writers]]\n[[Category:Hebrew-language writers]]\n[[Category:18th-century male writers]]\n\n\n{{Judaism-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "'''Aaron ben Isaac of [[Rechnitz]]''' was the author of a midrashic commentary on the Bible, the first portion of which (Genesis) was published in 1786 at [[Sulzbach-Rosenberg|Sulzbach]] under the title \"Bet Aharon\" (House of Aaron).<ref>{{JewishEncyclopedia|inline=1|article=AARON BEN ISAAC OF RECHNITZ|url=http://www.jewishencyclopedia.com/articles/44-aaron-ben-isaac-of-rechnitz|author=Louis Ginzberg|authorlink=Louis Ginzberg|accessdate=Oct 16, 2017}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:ben Isaac of Rechnitz, Aaron}}\n[[Category:18th-century German writers]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n[[Category:German Jews]]\n[[Category:German biblical scholars]]\n[[Category:18th-century Jews]]\n[[Category:Authors of Rabbinic works]]\n[[Category:Bible commentators]]\n[[Category:German male writers]]\n[[Category:Hebrew-language writers]]\n[[Category:18th-century male wri