{"title_page": "Ya\u011f\u0131z Kaba", "text_new": "{{short description|Turkish basketball player}}\n{{Infobox basketball biography\n| name = Ya\u011f\u0131z Kaba\n| image = \n| league = [[Turkish Basketball League|TBL]]\n| height_ft = 6\n| height_in = 3\n| weight_lbs =\n| position = [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]]\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1989|8|7}}\n| birth_place = [[Konak, Izmir|Konak]], [[Turkey]]\n| death_date =\n| death_place =\n| team = [[Be\u015fikta\u015f Cola Turka]]\n| college =\n| nationality = {{TUR}}\n| draft =\n| draft_team =\n| draft_year =\n| career_start = 2008\n| awards =\n}}\n\n'''Nasuhi Ya\u011f\u0131z Kaba''' (born 7 August 1989) is a [[Turkey|Turkish]] professional basketball player. He currently plays for [[Be\u015fikta\u015f Cola Turka]].<ref>http://www.tbl.org.tr/tb2l/oyuncu.asp?Kod=3895</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.tblstat.net/pd.asp?p=5 Player Profile]\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kaba, Yagiz}}\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Turkish men's basketball players]]\n[[Category:Be\u015fikta\u015f men's basketball players]]\n[[Category:Guards (basketball)]]\n\n\n{{Turkey-basketball-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Turkish basketball player}}\n{{Infobox basketball biography\n| name = Ya\u011f\u0131z Kaba\n| image = \n| league = [[Turkish Basketball League|TBL]]\n| height_ft = 6\n| height_in = 3\n| weight_lbs =\n| position = [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]]\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1989|8|7}}\n| birth_place = [[Konak, Izmir|Konak]], [[Turkey]]\n| death_date =\n| death_place =\n| team = [[Be\u015fikta\u015f Cola Turka]]\n| college =\n| nationality = {{TUR}}\n| draft =\n| draft_team =\n| draft_year =\n| career_start = 2008\n| awards =\n}}\n\n'''Nasuhi Ya\u011f\u0131z Kaba''' (born 7 August 1989) is a [[Turkey|Turkish]] professional basketball player. He currently plays for [[Be\